summary: I just had a thought! In Spider-Man: Far From Home, Fury says “nice to finally meet you.” I saw some people talking about how it...
body:
I just had a thought! In Spider-Man: Far From Home, Fury says “nice to finally meet you.” I saw some people talking about how it was Tony blocking Fury all these years, but then I remembered something…

Nick Fury is the one that recruited Richard Parker -AKA, Peter’s dad- to join the CIA! What if Fury had been keeping an eye on Peter all these years???

summary: Designed my own Miles for the Bold comics! He and Peter both fight crime in NY together for a long time before Bold Jumper...
caption: Designed my own Miles for the Bold comics! He and Peter both fight crime in NY together for a long time before Bold Jumper becomes part of the picture. They are both still Spider-Man, but Peter is referred to as Amazing Spider-Man and Miles is the Ultimate Spider-Man. The two are often just called Amazing or Ultimate for short! (Miles is also sometimes referred to as “the cooler Spider-Man”) This Miles is in his mid 20’s and doing great.
